msgid "oTree Setup (text editor)"
msgstr "安装oTree（文本编辑器）"

#: ../../source/install-nostudio.rst:8
msgid ""
"Note: it's recommended to use `oTree Studio <https://www.otreehub.com/"
"studio>`__ since it is specifically designed for building oTree apps. You "
"can easily switch to using a text editor later, by downloading your code."
msgstr ""
"注意：推荐使用 `oTree Studio <https://www.otreehub.com/studio>`__ ，这是为"
"构建oTree应用而专门设计的。你可以方便地在之后换为使用文本编辑器，下载你的"
"代码即可。"

